{"tid":1253001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(美軍可以來了!) 美國網民6.12路過金鐘中槍幸手機救命 轟港警策劃「暴動」","createTime":"2019-06-23T10:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T13:24:14.000Z","uid":239205,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9cfa918b7df6d939a6632db3f187a1441dadf22a","tid":1253001,"uid":239205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:28:17.000Z","msg":"再有更多片段顯示，6.12金鐘衝突警方衝着沒有暴動的市民施加不對等武力。有美國網民在YouTube發放影片，表示當日下午在夏慤道行車天橋為被催淚彈擊中眼睛的傷者洗眼時，被橡膠子彈擊中左大腿；幸得褲袋內手機擋下子彈，才免於一難。他形容這是一場由香港警方策劃出來的「暴動」，並接受傳媒訪問時表示「當日猶如戰場」。<br />\n<br />\n美國網民以賬戶「siliconfist」發佈影片，顯示他6.12當日在大批示威者在夏慤道行車天橋，目擊警方的清場行動。期間警方接連發射催淚彈及橡膠子彈，其中一發擊中他的左大腿。之後他取出手機並說「they fxxking shot me, they shot me﹗」他在影片介紹述及，那部手機已被粉碎（killed），但就保住了他的腳。其間有不少年輕示威者向「siliconfist」提供協助及了解其傷勢<br />\n<br />\n《香江日報》刊登該位美國網民的訪問指，他事後發現左腳仍有一個直徑5吋的圓形瘀傷，但無嚴重受傷。他形容當時防暴警察對準人群開槍及施放催淚彈，眾人均不忿而指罵他們。他稱，當日只是「路過」金鐘，但就目睹了香港的崩壞，並指若人民不能用選票表態，也會用腳步、金錢表態。他也說，這種警察暴行可能導致外商大舉離港。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190623/59748297?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190623%2F59748297%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr163e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=161a91c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190623%2F59748297%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=6cea18c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190623/59748297?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n美軍來了 大家一齊帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09e305f9f92f2ab7dcf9bf92f56b90ba8cbe2fe","tid":1253001,"uid":82068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T10:42:47.000Z","msg":"美軍來了我帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce0f71a1a59322d7596955a7748f2dfeaf2d2f9","tid":1253001,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:22:09.000Z","msg":"SEND 去美媒啦"},{"pid":"9c390a2b4debbcd2478f3dbb38c154f922a9349d","tid":1253001,"uid":195485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:23:16.000Z","msg":"你今次仲唔死?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c69d12385cd0f0684863ca2ceff1f8f70500a397","tid":1253001,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:24:14.000Z","msg":"只要有西媒報就可以炒大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}